Class Summary
Main  
MakeSummaryTable This class reads the table created after reading the input file, and constructs a new table that contains the aggregate values of various attributes grouped by states and political parties.

MP This class declares a datatype representing a member of parliament, containing all the details of an MP.
ReadFile This class reads the input data file, in Excel format, into a Prefuse Table.
StateMenu This class creates a Fisheye Menu visualisation of all the states.
TreeMap This class is responsible for creating a TreeMap visualisation of the given dataset.
TreeMap.BorderColorAction Set the stroke color for drawing treemap node outlines.
TreeMap.FillColorAction Set fill colors for treemap nodes.
TreeMap.LabelLayout Set label positions.
TreeMap.NodeRenderer A renderer for treemap nodes.
